com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5%2F255591%2F01%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%82%8A%E7%95%8C%E5%A4%B1%E5%AE%88-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%BC%81%E6%B0%91%E7%A9%BA%E7%BE%A4%E8%B6%8A%E5%A2%83-%E9%81%95%E7%A6%81%E6%BC%81%E5%85%B7%E7%A6%8D%E5%AE%B3%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AAWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=78834635\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01偵查/255591/01獨家-香港邊界失守-內地漁民空群越境-違禁漁具禍害海洋</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【邊界失守】水警僅遣返內地漁民　屢涉偷捕走私　議員批港府懶理<br />\n<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-11-15 21:00<br />\n<br />\n內地漁民在香港偷捕日益猖獗，有內地漁民及私梟更利用香港水域監管鬆懈的漏洞，屢次越境走私。有漁業界表示每日有50至100隻內地漁船在港捕魚，多在流浮山及大嶼山一帶出沒，有業界更曾聽聞有內地人士乘快艇來港搬貨走私內地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01偵查/256816/邊界失守-水警僅遣返內地漁民-屢涉偷捕走私-議員批港府懶理\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5%2F256816%2F%E9%82%8A%E7%95%8C%E5%A4%B1%E5%AE%88-%E6%B0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%83%85%E9%81%A3%E8%BF%94%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%BC%81%E6%B0%91-%E5%B1%A2%E6%B6%89%E5%81%B7%E6%8D%95%E8%B5%B0%E7%A7%81-%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%89%B9%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%87%B6%E7%90%86&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AAWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=15ecc4b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01偵查/256816/邊界失守-水警僅遣返內地漁民-屢涉偷捕走私-議員批港府懶理</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25bf80c28dfd7f82fc38ec10bc0e7ff8b1fb146","tid":1081801,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b60e813703e4011cc9f8fef4725e90124d6d2fb7","tid":1081801,"uid":21194,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"d094a6ae8595fd8d53e831d79d18164b4a7eea77","tid":1081801,"uid":39013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a1e96673bed0751c144ee24e77d8536c63e2213","tid":1081801,"uid":21194,"like":2,"dislike":45,"score":-43,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"唔好吹大d 一